Title: agent_vsphere: wrongly configured connection timeout leads to high CPU usage
Level: 1
Component: checks
Compatible: compat
Edition: cre
Version: 1.6.0p28
Date: 1638192927
Class: fix

The special agent for vSphere did not have a properly configured connection
timeout. This lead to several long-running agent_vsphere processes that
consumed a lot of CPU. This has been fixed.
